Preheat oven to 375 degrees F (190 degrees C). Thoroughly cream together shortening, sugars, eggs and vanilla. In a separate bowl, mix together the dry ingredients, except the candies. Add to creamed mixture and mix well. Stir in 1/2 cup candies. Mix well. Drop by teaspoon unto cookie sheets and decorate with remaining candies. Bake for 10 - 12 minutes.